      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases relevant to blood pump flows.",
      "rationale": "The solver was verified against the ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmarks. Convergence to analytical solutions was demonstrated for laminar and transitional flow regimes applicable to centrifugal pump internal flows."
