      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal input values and sources must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (3.5 mPa·s), density (1060 kg/m³), and inlet boundary conditions were sourced from device specifications and published physiological ranges. Sensitivity to input variation is not formally assessed at MRL 2. All input values and their sources are documented in the simulation input record."
