      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; number of experimental replicates must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Three replicate experiments were conducted at each of the 5 operating points using separate blood fills. Variability across replicates was within ±6% for NIH. Formal statistical characterization of sample-to-sample variability is not required at MRL 2 but is noted as supporting evidence."
